<br>
Yesterday while in Plane of Fear with my guild, I noticed all my spells (level 4-61) were being haste focused.  I was not wearing any spell haste focus item though.  I tried taking off all my gear one at a time and testing, no change.  Then I took off all my gear and tested, the effect was gone.  When I put back on all my gear it stayed gone.<br>
<br>
Last night in Plane of Disease I was pulling soloing mobs with Firebolt of Tallon and aggro kite.  I had the sapphire bracer on for damage focus.  When the mobs were on flat ground with me, the bracer would focus.  When they were on the side of a hill and I was bolting them, the bolt would land for 1920 every time.  (the un-focused damage of FoT at 61).<br>
<br>
